ord, The Greco-Persian Wars is a book that lovers of fine historical writing will greet with pleasure.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aSalamis, Battle of, Greece, 480 B.C. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh  a1970s.  aacademic.  aancient history.  aancient world.  abibliography.  acreativity.  ademocracy.  ageographical.  agreco persian.  agreece.  agreek empire.  agreek studies.  agreek.  ahistory ancient greece.  ahistory of ancient greece.  aindependence.  ainspiring.  ainternational.  amilitary history.  amilitary.  apersian empire.  apolitical science.  aregional.  areissue.  ascholarly.  asocial science.  asocial studies.  asoldiers.  aupdated.  awar history.  awartime.  aworld history.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000z978311063534840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052091706440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520917064423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520917064/original  a978-3-11-063534-8  University of California Press Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles